<center><div class="typewriter"><h3><center><strong class="glowsmall">SEGMENT YOUR TASKS.</strong></center><ul class="glowblue"><li>FOUNDATIONAL means NO task comes before.</li>
<li>INTERMEDIARY means tasks will come before and after.</li>
